  <metadata>
    <name>VIE-L2 — Wachau Valley Weekend Loop</name>
    <desc>Deploy from VIE and ride into the Wachau Valley. Hit Dürnstein Castle Viewpoint — 310m and Jauerling Summit Road — 960m. Loop back to VIE over a packed 2–3 day weekend escape. No highways, just curves and elevation.</desc>
